Title: Armored Carp
Description:
Armored Carp are a delicacy around these parts.

Unfortunately we can't fish them up since they snap our hooks with their powerful jaws.  Take this fishing spear and see if you can catch a few for us.
ObjectivesText: Use the Fishing Spear to catch 5 Armored Carp in the waters south of Anglers Wharf.
PortraitGiverText: Hooks won't work on this one.
